@startuml
title 登录与受保护页面鉴权顺序图
actor "用户" as User
participant "LoginView.vue" as Login
participant "authStore" as Store
participant "auth.js / request.js" as API
participant "auth router" as AuthRouter
participant "JWT Security" as Security
database "SQLite users" as DB
participant "Vue Router Guard" as Guard
participant "Protected View" as View

User -> Login: 输入 username/password
Login -> Store: login(credentials)
Store -> API: POST /api/auth/login
API -> AuthRouter: JSON username/password
AuthRouter -> DB: 查询用户
AuthRouter -> Security: verify_password()
Security --> AuthRouter: valid
AuthRouter -> Security: create_access_token(user.id)
Security --> AuthRouter: access_token
AuthRouter --> API: success data token/user
API --> Store: token/user
Store -> Store: 保存 localStorage
Store --> Login: session
Login -> Guard: router.replace(/dashboard)
Guard -> Store: isAuthenticated?
Guard -> Store: fetchCurrentUser if needed
Store -> API: GET /api/auth/me
API -> AuthRouter: Authorization Bearer token
AuthRouter -> Security: decode_access_token()
Security --> AuthRouter: sub/exp
AuthRouter -> DB: 查询 active user
AuthRouter --> API: current user
API --> Store: user
Guard --> View: 放行受保护页面

alt token 缺失或无效
  Guard --> Login: redirect /login
end
@enduml
